profile:
Oncor Industrial Services is located inTimmins, Ontario and was established in April 2010 to provide Dry Ice BlastCleaning andPolyurethane Spray Foam Insulation services to the Residential. Industrial and Commercial markets in All of Ontario.
We are committed to providing professional service, competitive pricing, quality materials and superior workmanship in every job and task we undertake.
We will always remain true to our founding values of honesty, quality and hard work, and are committed to the highest standards and integrity in delivering our services.
To ensure the best possible service for the Spray Foam Insulation business we have invested in the latest and most advanced equipment available today. Oncor Industrial Services has a 28ft custom designed SPRAY FOAM RIG with advanced spray foam application equipment capable of handling small residential projects to large industrial / institutional
projects.
